<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Testunau_cyfansawdd-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Testunau cyfansawdd&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Testunau cyfansawdd&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Testunau_cyfansawdd-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z"><span class="mw-headline" id="Testunau_cyfansawdd"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Testunau_cyfansawdd-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z"></span>Testunau cyfansawdd<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Testunau_cyfansawdd-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Golygu&#039;r adran: Testunau cyfansawdd"><span>golygu</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Testunau_cyfansawdd-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z","replies":["c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Llywelyn2000-2022-02-10T13:00:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z","timestamp":"2022-02-10T13:00:00.000Z"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Testunau_cyfansawdd-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Testunau cyfansawdd&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Testunau cyfansawdd&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd"></span>Mae Wicidestun Ffrangeg, yn cyhoeddi nifer o'i lyfrau dwywaith. Unwaith yn y ffordd draddodiadol efo tudalen trawsgrifio ar gyfer pob pennod / cerdd / erthygl etc ac wedyn eilwaith efo'r llyfr cyfan wedi ei drawsgrifio ar un tudalen. Eu rheswm dros wneud hyn yw er mwyn galluogi chwiliad o fewn llyfr yn fwy hylaw. Er enghraifft os ydwyf yn cofio bod cerdd am "bronfraith" yn Nhelynegion Maes a Môr, heb gofio teitl y gerdd, gallwn fynd at y testun cyfansawdd un tudalen a chwilio am y gair bronfraith trwy ddefnyddio Ctrl/F i gael hyd i'r gerdd yn haws na defnyddio'r chwiliad o bopeth sydd ar safle Wicidestun. Rwyf wedi gwneud arbrawf o'r ymarfer Ffrangeg ar Wicidestun Cymraeg efo testunau cyfansawdd o bedwar llyfr [<a class="external text" href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Categori:Testunau_cyfansawdd">Categori-Testunau cyfansawdd</a>] . Hoffwn wybod barn eraill am werth y fath ymarfer cyn bwrw ymlaen i wneud tudalennau tebyg ar gyfer gweddill y llyfrau rwyf wedi trawsgrifio. <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">AlwynapHuw</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">17:41, 9 Chwefror 2022 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z","author":"AlwynapHuw","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd","replies":["c-Llywelyn2000-2022-02-10T13:00:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-09T17:41:00.000Z-Testunau_cyfansawdd"></span>
</p>
