<dl><dd><a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000" title="Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-02-10T15:35:00.000Z"></span>Llywelyn2000</a> Yn ôl y rheolau Saesneg, dylid ddileu'r heiffen a chreu gair cyfan. Os yw heiffen yn croesi tudalen dylid rhoi y gair cyfan ar un dudalen yn hytrach na thori gair dros dwy dudalen <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">AlwynapHuw</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-02-10T15:35:00.000Z" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">06:23, 27 Chwefror 2022 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-02-10T15:35:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z","author":"AlwynapHuw","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-02-10T15:35:00.000Z","replies":["c-Llywelyn2000-2022-03-01T15:33:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-02-10T15:35:00.000Z"></span>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-03-01T15:33:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z"></span>Diolch Alwyn! Mae hynny'n synhwyrol! <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000" title="Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000">Llywelyn2000</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-Llywelyn2000-2022-03-01T15:33:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">15:33, 1 Mawrth 2022 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-03-01T15:33:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2022-03-01T15:33:00.000Z","author":"Llywelyn2000","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-Llywelyn2000-2022-03-01T15:33:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-03-01T15:33:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-02-27T06:23:00.000Z"></span></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-AlwynapHuw-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z-Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Oll synnwyr pen Kembero ygyd&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Oll synnwyr pen Kembero ygyd&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z"><span class="mw-headline" id="Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z"></span>Oll synnwyr pen Kembero ygyd<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Golygu&#039;r adran: Oll synnwyr pen Kembero ygyd"><span>golygu</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-AlwynapHuw-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z","replies":["c-AlwynapHuw-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z-Oll_synnwyr_pen_Kembero_ygyd"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:46:00.000Z-AlwynapHuw-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z","timestamp":"2022-04-04T13:46:00.000Z"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__2__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__2__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-2022-04-02T02:07:00.000Z