<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z-Cornel_Saesneg"></span>Dw i'n cynnig cael cornel i'r sbwriel canolog Saesneg, sy'n britho'r hen Sgriptoriwm, fel mai dim ond yr heniaith fydd yn cael ei defnyddio yma o hyn ymlaen. <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000" title="Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000">Llywelyn2000</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z-Cornel_Saesneg" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">13:49, 4 Ebrill 2022 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z-Cornel_Saesneg"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z","author":"Llywelyn2000","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z-Cornel_Saesneg","replies":["c-AlwynapHuw-2022-04-25T15:36:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z","c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:42:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-04T13:49:00.000Z-Cornel_Saesneg"></span>
</p>
