<p><a class="external text" href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Steward_requests/Permissions#AlwynapHuw@cyws"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z-Creu_Gweinyddwr_arall_ar_cy-wicidestun;_cais_2"></span>Cefnidir: cais ar Meta.</a>
</p><p>Carwn gynnig <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw</a> yn Weinyddwr ar yr wici yma (Wicidestun), gyda <span class="template-ping">@<a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:Mahagaja" title="Defnyddiwr:Mahagaja">Mahagaja</a>:</span>. Rhowch eich pleidlais neu sylwadau os gwelwch yn dda. Bydd y cyfle i gefnogi neu wrthod ar agor am gyfnod o 5 diwrnod. Diolch. <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000" title="Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000">Llywelyn2000</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:Llywelyn2000">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z-Creu_Gweinyddwr_arall_ar_cy-wicidestun;_cais_2" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">08:31, 27 Ebrill 2022 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z-Creu_Gweinyddwr_arall_ar_cy-wicidestun;_cais_2"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z","author":"Llywelyn2000","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z-Creu_Gweinyddwr_arall_ar_cy-wicidestun;_cais_2","replies":["c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:32:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z","c-Mahagaja-2022-04-27T09:08:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z","c-Brin_Rees-2022-04-28T02:32:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z","c-Craigysgafn-2022-04-28T09:11:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z","c-Llygadebrill-2022-04-29T18:29:00.000Z-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Llywelyn2000-2022-04-27T08:31:00.000Z-Creu_Gweinyddwr_arall_ar_cy-wicidestun;_cais_2"></span>
