<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Bookreader-20221007152600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Bookreader&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Bookreader&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Bookreader-20221007152600"><span class="mw-headline" id="Bookreader"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Bookreader-20221007152600"></span>Bookreader<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Bookreader-20221007152600"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Golygu&#039;r adran: Bookreader"><span>golygu</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Bookreader-20221007152600","replies":["c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader","timestamp":"20221007152600"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Bookreader-20221007152600&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Bookreader&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Bookreader&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader"></span>Rwyf wedi gosod nodwedd newydd ar Wicidestun, rwy'n gobeithio bydd yn ategu at werth y safle. Ar ddiwedd llinell teitl pob tudalen <b>indecs</b> mae 'na icon bach bellach, sy'n edrych fel dau dudalen o lyfr.
</p>
<figure class="mw-halign-center" typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/Delwedd:Icon_Bookreader.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Icon_Bookreader.jpg/500px-Icon_Bookreader.jpg" decoding="async" width="500" height="66" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Icon_Bookreader.jpg/750px-Icon_Bookreader.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Icon_Bookreader.jpg/1000px-Icon_Bookreader.jpg 2x" data-file-width="2825" data-file-height="375"/></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>O roi clec ar yr icon bydd modd mynd i safle Wikimedia Bookreader a darllen unrhyw lyfr sydd wedi uwchlwytho yma, boed wedi ei drawsysgrifio neu beidio, fel rhith lyfr.
Mantais hyn yw ei fod yn golygu bod gwerth inni rŵan gosod llyfrau sydd yn rhy fawr i obeithio y caent eu trawsysgrifio am flynyddoedd maith, megis 10 cyfrol (9,000 tudalen, 11 miliwn gair)
<a href="/wiki/Categori:Y_Gwyddoniadur_Cymreig" title="Categori:Y Gwyddoniadur Cymreig">Y Gwyddoniadur Cymreig</a> Dr John Parry a Thomas Gee. Rwyf wedi creu tudalen sy'n cynnwys rhestr o'r holl dudalennau <b>Indecs</b> <a href="/wiki/Rhestr_o_dudalennau_Indecs" title="Rhestr o dudalennau Indecs">Rhestr o dudalennau Indecs</a> ac rwyf wrthi'n rhoi categorïau testun ac awdur ar yr holl dudalennau indecs hefyd, fel bydd modd eu canfod trwy <a href="/wiki/Categori:Nofelau" title="Categori:Nofelau">Categori:Nofelau</a> <a href="/wiki/Categori:Owen_Morgan_Edwards" title="Categori:Owen Morgan Edwards">Categori:Owen Morgan Edwards</a> ac ati. <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">AlwynapHuw</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">15:26, 7 Hydref 2022 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20221007152600","author":"AlwynapHuw","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-AlwynapHuw-20221007152600-Bookreader"></span>
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Rhyswynne-20230612113700&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr-20230612113700&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Archif cylchgrawn Y Casglwr&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Archif cylchgrawn Y Casglwr&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr-20230612113700"><span class="mw-headline" id="Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr-20230612113700"></span>Archif cylchgrawn Y Casglwr<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr-20230612113700"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Golygu&#039;r adran: Archif cylchgrawn Y Casglwr"><span>golygu</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-Rhyswynne-20230612113700","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr-20230612113700","replies":["c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr","timestamp":"20230612113700"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-Rhyswynne-20230612113700&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr-20230612113700&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Archif cylchgrawn Y Casglwr&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Archif cylchgrawn Y Casglwr&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr"></span>Sylwaf bod cynnwys holl wefan Y Casglwr ar drwydded CY-BY-3.0, gan gynnwys <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.casglwr.org/yrarchif.html">archif o hen erthyglau</a> o 1977 lle maen't wedi dechrau eu digideiddio gan dddefnyddio OCR. Mae erthyglau 1977-1980 (a falle mwy) ar ffurff HTML sydd ond angen mân dwtio acenion. Gan gymryd bod y drwydded hon yn dderbyniol ar gyfer ailgynhyrchu <a href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Help:Licensing_compatibility#Creative_Commons_Attribution" class="extiw" title="en:Help:Licensing compatibility"> o edrych ar ganllawiau Wikisource</a>, dwi'n awyddus dechrau gyda'r gwaith o'u trosi yma, yn arbennig gan bod yr erthyglau, oherwydd diben Cymdeithas Bob Owen, yn frith o gyfeiriadau at hen lyfrau, rhai mae'n ddigon posib sydd eisoes ar Wicidestun, gan gynnig cyfle i gyfeirio at gynnwys sydd yma'n barod. Gwerthfawrogaf unrhyw sylwadau neu dips cyn imi ddechrau arni, ac mae'n siwr bydd gennyf gwestiynau wrth fynd ati gan mod i'n ddibrofiad yma. <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:Rhyswynne" title="Defnyddiwr:Rhyswynne">Rhyswynne</a> (<a href="/w/index.php?title=Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:Rhyswynne&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:Rhyswynne (dim tudalen ar gael)">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">11:37, 12 Mehefin 2023 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20230612113700","author":"Rhyswynne","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Rhyswynne-20230612113700-Archif_cylchgrawn_Y_Casglwr"></span>
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024-20231206152100&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Awduron rhydd o hawlfraint 2024&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Awduron rhydd o hawlfraint 2024&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024-20231206152100"><span class="mw-headline" id="Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024-20231206152100"></span>Awduron rhydd o hawlfraint 2024<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024-20231206152100"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Golygu&#039;r adran: Awduron rhydd o hawlfraint 2024"><span>golygu</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024-20231206152100","replies":["c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024","timestamp":"20231206152100"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024-20231206152100&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Awduron rhydd o hawlfraint 2024&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Awduron rhydd o hawlfraint 2024&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024"></span>Yn ôl y ddeddf, mae cyhoeddiad yn dod yn rhydd o hawlfraint ar y 1af o Ionawr 70 mlynedd ar ôl farwolaeth yr awdur. Felly bydd llyfrau ac ati gan awduron a fu farw yn ystod 1953 yn symud i'r parth cyhoeddus ac yn rhydd i'w cyhoeddi ar Wicidestun. Ymysg yr awduron Cymraeg a fu farw ym 1953 mae :-
</p>
<ul><li><a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Winnie_Parry" class="extiw" title="w:Winnie Parry">Winnie Parry</a>. (mae <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:Craigysgafn" title="Defnyddiwr:Craigysgafn">Craigysgafn</a> wedi trawsysgrifio un o'i llyfrau hi, Cerrig y Rhyd, yn barod a bydd yn cael ei gyhoeddi o fewn munudau i glychau 'r flwyddyn Newydd ganu yn Seland Newydd.</li>
<li><a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellen_Evans" class="extiw" title="w:Ellen Evans">Ellen Evans</a></li>
<li>Bu farw <a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Lewis_(ysgolhaig)" class="extiw" title="w:Thomas Lewis (ysgolhaig)">Thomas Lewis</a> a'i frawd <a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Howell_Elvet_Lewis_(Elfed)" class="extiw" title="w:Howell Elvet Lewis (Elfed)">Elfed</a> o fewn ychydig misoedd i'w gilydd ym 1953.</li>
<li><a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Mardy_Rees" class="extiw" title="w:Thomas Mardy Rees">T Mardy Rees</a></li>
<li><a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elizabeth_Mary_Jones_(Moelona)" class="extiw" title="w:Elizabeth Mary Jones (Moelona)">Moelona</a>. Rwyf wedi paratoi chwech o'i nofelau hi i'w cyhoeddi yn gynnar yn y flwyddyn Newydd-Beryl, Breuddwydion Myfanwy, Bugail y Bryn, Ffynonloyw, Plant y goedwig, a'r Lleian Lwyd ond rwy'n methu yn fy myw cael gafael o gopi o'i nofel enwocaf Teulu Bach Nantoer a gyhoeddwyd cyn 1953</li>
<li><a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Glyn_Davies" class="extiw" title="w:John Glyn Davies">John Glyn Davies</a> (Oes gan unrhyw un copïau cynnar o'i lyfrau caneuon Cerddi Huw Puw 1923, Cerddi Robin Goch 1935 a Cherddi Portinllaen 1936)?</li></ul>
<p>Ac ymysg yr awduron Eingl-gymreig <a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dylan_Thomas" class="extiw" title="w:Dylan Thomas">Dylan Thomas</a> ac <a href="https://cy.wikipedia.org/wiki/Idris_Davies" class="extiw" title="w:Idris Davies">Idris Davies</a>.
</p><p>Os oes gynnoch chi lyfrau ar eich silff gan rai o'r awduron hyn (neu eraill a bu farw cyn Rhagfyr 31 1953) a modd i'w gopïo fel ffeiliau PDF efo printer 3 yn 1 neu app ffôn uwch lwythwch nhw ar Gomin er mwyn eu rhannu a'r byd. <a href="/wiki/Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">AlwynapHuw</a> (<a href="/wiki/Sgwrs_Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw" title="Sgwrs Defnyddiwr:AlwynapHuw">sgwrs</a>) <a href="https://cy.wikisource.org/wiki/Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm#c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">15:21, 6 Rhagfyr 2023 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">ateb</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"20231206152100","author":"AlwynapHuw","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-AlwynapHuw-20231206152100-Awduron_rhydd_o_hawlfraint_2024"></span>
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2 ext-discussiontools-init-section"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONDESKTOP__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting-20240422122100&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Invitation to join April Wikisource Community Meeting&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Invitation to join April Wikisource Community Meeting&quot;}--><h2 data-mw-thread-id="h-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting-20240422122100"><span class="mw-headline" id="Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting-20240422122100"></span>Invitation to join April Wikisource Community Meeting<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting-20240422122100"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wicidestun:Y_Sgriptoriwm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Golygu&#039;r adran: Invitation to join April Wikisource Community Meeting"><span>golygu</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"headingLevel":2,"name":"h-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100","type":"heading","level":0,"id":"h-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting-20240422122100","replies":["c-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting"]}}--><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-bar"><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-metadata"><!--__DTLATESTCOMMENTTHREAD__{"id":"c-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting","timestamp":"20240422122100"}__--><!--__DTCOMMENTCOUNT__1__--><!--__DTAUTHORCOUNT__1__--></div><div class="ext-discussiontools-init-section-actions"><!--__DTSUBSCRIBEBUTTONMOBILE__{&quot;headingLevel&quot;:2,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;h-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heading&quot;,&quot;level&quot;:0,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;h-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting-20240422122100&quot;,&quot;replies&quot;:[&quot;c-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting&quot;],&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Invitation to join April Wikisource Community Meeting&quot;,&quot;linkableTitle&quot;:&quot;Invitation to join April Wikisource Community Meeting&quot;}--></div></div></div>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-MediaWiki_message_delivery-20240422122100-Invitation_to_join_April_Wikisource_Community_Meeting"></span>Hello fellow Wikisource enthusiasts!
</p><p><br/>
We are the hosting this month’s Wikisource Community meeting on <b>27 April 2024, 7 AM UTC</b> (<a class="external text" href="https://zonestamp.toolforge.org/1714201200">check your local time</a>).
</p><p><br/>
Similar to previous meetings, the agenda will be split into two segments. The first half will cover non-technical updates, such as events, conferences, proofread-a-thons, and collaborations. In the second half, we'll dive into technical updates and discussions, addressing key challenges faced by Wikisource communities.
</p><p>Simply follow the link below to secure your spot and engage with fellow Wikisource enthusiasts:
</p><p><a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Event:Wikisource_Community_Meeting_April_2024" class="extiw" title="m:Event:Wikisource Community Meeting April 2024">Event Registration Page</a>
</p><p>If you have any suggestions or would just prefer being added to the meeting the old way,
simply drop a message on <b>klawal-ctr@wikimedia.org</b>. 
</p><p>Thank you for your continued dedication to Wikisource. We look forward to your active participation in our upcoming meeting.
</p><p>Regards
<a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:KLawal-WMF" class="extiw" title="m:User:KLawal-WMF">KLawal-WMF</a>, <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:SWilson_(WMF)" class="extiw" title="m:User:SWilson (WMF)">Sam Wilson (WMF)</a>, and <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:SGill_(WMF)" class="extiw" title="m:User:SGill (WMF)">Satdeep Gill (WMF)</a>
</p><p><br/>
